WEBVTT

30:28.149 --> 30:30.983
No matter how much you polish copper,
it won't become gold, Georgekutty.

30:30.983 --> 30:32.608
Instead of tinkering
with this old house,

30:32.816 --> 30:35.358
why not build a new one?
How many times have I told you?

30:35.483 --> 30:36.483
Hey, you, come here!
